The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | Sports | In the City
                                                                                                               IN THE CITY
                  
	 Mohun Bagan are all set to rope in Kalighats Anushtup Majumdar and Sandip Sanyal for the upcoming cricket season. Bagan have also roped in Subhomoy Das. Kalighat, on the other hand, have taken pacer Sourav Sarkar from East Bengal. Md Ziauddin and Mannu Kumar will play for Town Club.                
	 Abhra Mondal, the East Bengal goalkeeper, has signed for the club for a third consecutive season.                
	 Tennis: AITA Talent series from 9am and BTA Junior meet from 3pm at the Calcutta Punjab Club                                                                                                                                                                       
